highlights.text: Hindia has the most spots on Top Songs Indonesia. “everything u are” is the highest at #5.
“Lihat Kebunku (Taman Bunga)” by Aku Jeje is the highest new entry on Top Songs Indonesia at #181.
“Untuk Perempuan Yang Sedang Di Pelukan” by Payung Teduh has been on Top Songs Indonesia the longest, at 3190 days straight.
“Kenangan Manis” by Pamungkas is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Indonesia, up 47 spots at #100.
